gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Hello there!\n"
	.string "Welcome to the POKéMON-Lottery.\l"
	.string "have you participated before? Let me\l"
	.string "quickly explain what this is all about.\p"
	.string "Each week I, BIRCH the POKéMON\n"
	.string "PROFESSOR, give away one of three\l"
	.string "POKéMON to a random person who has\l"
	.string "entered the draw.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This is the prize POKéMON last week's\n"
	.string "winner chose from their selection.\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "It's a LOTAD, a Grass-Water Type which\n"
	.string "will evolve twice if raised well, that\l"
	.string "theme follows through with all our\l"
	.string "giveaways.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "Meaning the winner and their POKéMON\n"
	.string "have the chance to grow closer and\l"
	.string "stronger alongside each other,\l"
	.string "resulting in better battle synergies.\p"
	.string "...\p"
	.string "...well that's the theory I am trying to\n"
	.string "prove.\p"
	.string "$"

