	.string "Alright that's all the info we need.\n"
	.string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN} who's just about to\l"
	.string "move from PETALBURG CITY to\l"
	.string "LITTLEROOT. Thanks for the\l"
	.string "registration. Make sure to tune in when\l"
	.string "we announce the winner live on TV.\p"
